{"tid":1267152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好比機會任何人將你嘅聲音抹殺！","createTime":"2019-06-29T17:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T18:14:28.000Z","uid":203367,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eedb1d1fa9be4e4fa2614002f5ae93cfe6fe34a0","tid":1267152,"uid":203367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"今日返到屋企睇新聞之後成晚瞓唔着<br />\n好想同大家講返少少野<br />\n亦都想抒發下自己嘅感受<br />\n<br />\n大家經過 69 612 等等等等直到今日<br />\n發現無論和平示威遊行 定衝擊立法會各種方法都試過<br />\n無論用任何方法政府都係一個wfc既態度 <br />\n好多人都開始灰心好絕望 <br />\n想用盡地一搏嘅方式黎守護我哋呢個咁愛嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n但記住 錯嘅係佢哋唔係我哋！<br />\n唔值得因為佢哋嘅錯誤而賠上自己條命<br />\n<br />\n同埋冷漠啲講就算你死咗佢哋都唔會care<br />\n分分鐘仲暗暗開心緊少咗個人喺度阻住佢哋<br />\n<br />\n你死咗佢鍾意點講就點講<br />\n甚至完全違背你嘅意願會用嚟大做文章！！<br />\n你連為自己辯駁嘅機會都無！<br />\n<br />\n所以我喺度誠懇希望大家留返條命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行出黎 企出黎</strong></span> </span><br />\n直到佢哋無任何嘅方法再去漠視我地 <br />\n直到我哋爭取到我哋想要嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我哋真係一個都不能少！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"57ab1c6fae6bd780dc934fdf1d720e843b525858","tid":1267152,"uid":5680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oco4HuS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOco4HuS.gif&h=b6fd3e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a784908a65f3cf37493b6b1121fe90636f1198e5","tid":1267152,"uid":203367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:14:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好令親者痛 仇者快</strong></span></span>"}]}